column5: Anyone here about man falling threw the ice today at pete's point??just wondering on an update???
From what I just read he was a 49 year old Napanee man...happened around Hay's Bay on Quinte.  Condolences to his family.
Sadly, the Quinte Fishing board confirms the body of a 49 year old man was recovered by police.  No other details there. Condolences to the family. Michael
